@AuthenticationServiceApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:8083

### Register a new user
POST {{AuthenticationServiceApi_HostAddress}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login with existing user
POST {{AuthenticationServiceApi_HostAddress}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}
